build entity.o: cc Entity.cpp
build entityhandler.o: cc EntityHandler.cpp
build player.o: cc Player.cpp
build chunk.o: cc Chunk.cpp
build shader.o: cc Shader.cpp
build utils.o: cc Utils.cpp
build chunkshader.o: cc ChunkShader.cpp
build game.o: cc Game.cpp
